text:
Hello──... Oh,
you came by last time too, right?

Yeah, thank you always...
...Come visit again sometime?

(Seems like she's good
at interacting with fans.)

Good job, Hana.
Today's event went really well, didn't it...?!

Really?
Ahaha, I'm glad you think so, Producer.

...After talking to Hana,
the customers all seemed really happy.

I was really happy
talking to everyone too, so...
Surely, we share the same feelings, right?
